  <brief_title>A Study to Assess the Safety, Tolerability and Clinical Activity of TD−1211 in Patients With Opioid-Induced Constipation</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Phase 2, Randomized, Double-Blind, Placebo-Controlled, Dose-Escalation Study to Assess the Safety, Tolerability, and Clinical Activity of TD−1211 in Subjects With Opioid-Induced Constipation</official_title>
